title: The Snellster
description:
Steve Snell returns to The Kirk Minihane Show. Troy Aikman is criticized online for saying the NFL needs to "take off their dresses" (00:14:00). Rico Bosco produced a blogging masterpiece (00:30:00). Toucher and Rich address their producer being laid off (00:33:00). John Oliver wasn't to cancel football but Kirk points out it's interesting he's never tried to cancel boxing. Kirk casts Emma Stone to play Kelly Keegs, calls & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
